Package main.java.com.djrapitops.plan.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalysisData
    This class is used to store result data from Analysis at runtime.
    DemographicsData
    This class is used to store Demographics data inside the UserData.
    KillData
    This class is used to store data about a player kill inside the UserData object.
    RawAnalysisData
    This class is used for storing combined data of several UserData objects during Analysis and thus is not documented.
    SessionData
    This class is used for storing start and end of a playsession inside UserData object.
    UserData
    This class is used for storing information about a player during runtime.
